{{Infobox economy|continent=Africa|population=1.307 billion (16%; 2019)<ref name="2013 World Population Data Sheet" />|Governing body=African Union|Head quarters=Addis Ababa|Largest city=Lagos|gdp={{nowrap|$2.6 trillion ([[List of continents by GDP (nominal)|Nominal]]; 2019)<ref name="IMF GDP"/><br />$6.7 trillion (PPP; 2019)<ref name="IMF GDP">{{cite web|title=GDP Nominal and PPP Data, current prices  |url=https://www.imf.org/external/datamapper/NGDPD@WEO/OEMDC/ADVEC/WEOWORLD/AFQ |publisher=International Monetary Fund|date=2018|accessdate=6 March 2020}}</ref> }}|per capita=$1,970 (2020; [[List of continents by GDP (nominal)#GDP per capita .28nominal.29 by continents|6th]])<ref name="IMF GDP"/>|growth=3.7%<ref name="IMF GDP"/>|millionaires=140,000 (0.011%)|unemployment=15%|footnote=Most numbers are from the [[International Monetary Fund]].}}'''Ubukungu bwa Afrika''' bugizwe nubucuruzi, inganda, ubuhinzi, hamwe nabakozi bo [[Afurika|kumugabane]] . Mu mwaka wi 2019 ,  ibihugu 54 bigize umugabane wa Afurika byari bituwe n'abantu bagera kuri miliyari 1,3  . Afurika ni umugabane ukungahaye ku mutungo.   Iterambere rya vuba ryatewe no kwiyongera kugurisha ibicuruzwa, serivisi, ninganda.  Biteganijwe ko umwaka wa 2050 uzagera; Afurika y'Iburengerazuba, Afurika y'Iburasirazuba, Afurika yo hagati na Afurika y'Epfo by'umwihariko, bigeze kuri GDP ingana na tiriyari 29 z'amadorari. 

Muri Werurwe 2013, Afurika yagaragaye nk'umugabane ukennye cyane ku isi: Umusaruro rusange wa Afurika wose hamwe ni kimwe cya gatatu cy'umusaruro rusange w'Amerika; ariko, Banki y'Isi iteganya ko ibihugu byinshi by'Afurika bizagera ku "rwego rwo hagati" (nukuvuga nibura US $ 1.000 ku muntu ku mwaka) mu 2025 niba umuvuduko w'ubwiyongere ukomeje.  Hariho impamvu zitari nke zituma ubukungu bwifashe nabi muri Afurika: mu mateka, Afurika yari ifite ingoma nyinshi zikize zicuruza ibice byinshi byisi; icyakora, ubukoloni bw’ibihugu by’i Burayi hamwe n’ibibazo byakurikiyeho byatewe na decolonisation kandi bikabije n’intambara y'ubutita, byateje ibidukikije bidahungabana mu bukungu no mu mibereho. 
